----------------------------------------------------------------------------
|  02 - FIRST PROGRAM                                                      |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

- First Program

    #include <stdio.h>

    int main(void) {
        printf("Programming is fun.\n");
    
        return 0;
    }



- Compiling and Running First Program

    # Compile with standard Unix compiler
    $ cc prog1.c

    # Compile with gcc
    $ gcc prog1.c


    # Run executable file
    $ ./a.out


    # Create custom name for executable
    $ gcc prog1.c -o prog1



- Displaying the Value of Variables

    int value1, value2, sum;

    value1 = 50;
    value2 = 25;
    sum = value1 + value2;

    printf("The sum of %i and %i is %i\n", value1, value2, sum);



